ygData.messageBody:
Bio of Ehlanna Winterlark (Bristlebain), and
Ehlissa (E'ci) - [Ehlanna was taken when I signed on.]

Ehlanna brushes a strand of hair from her face, winks, and flashes you an impish
smile.
"Hiyas, sugar, buy a girl a drink? I'm sure I have a tune or two you would
like."
